<Legal
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Tiximo is an independent event discovery service, not affiliated with any ticketing platform."
>
  <section>
    <h2>Independence</h2>
    <p>Tiximo is an independent event discovery service and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or partnered with Ticketmaster, Live Nation, Eventbrite, DICE, or any other ticketing platform or event organiser.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Event data</h2>
    <p>All event data is sourced via publicly available APIs provided by third-party platforms. Tiximo does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or currency of any event information displayed. Event details — including dates, times, venues, and ticket availability — may change without notice.</p>
    <p>Always verify event details directly with the event organiser or ticketing platform before purchasing tickets.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Bookings</h2>
    <p>All ticket purchases are completed on the respective provider's platform under their terms and conditions. Tiximo has no involvement in the booking process and cannot process refunds, exchanges, or disputes.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Referral commission</h2>
    <p>Tiximo earns a referral commission on some purchases at no extra cost to you. This does not influence the events we recommend — rankings are based on relevance to you.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Ticket support</h2>
    <p>For ticket support, refunds, or disputes — contact your ticket provider directly:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Ticketmaster: <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/help" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ticketmaster.com/help</a></li>
      <li>Eventbrite: <a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/support" target="_blank" rel="noopener">eventbrite.com/support</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Legal>
